dublin_core.dcvalue: Cooperatives delivering out of hours care in the Netherlands are hesitant about the use of expert systems during triage Apart from the extra costs cooperatives are not sure that quality of triage is sufficiently enhanced by these systems and believe that call duration will be prolonged drastically No figures about the influence of the use of an expert system during triage on call duration and triage decisions in out of hours care in the Netherlands are available
Call-duration and triage decisions in out of hours cooperatives with and without the use of an expert system.
